          <h3>What is Geometry Dash?</h3>
          <p>Geometry Dash is a fast-paced platform game where you control a small cube that moves automatically from left to right. Your only job is to tap or click at the right moment to jump over spikes, gaps, and dangerous obstacles. There is no way to slow down or stop, so timing is everything. Each level is synchronized with an energetic soundtrack, and obstacles always appear in the same place, so repetition and memory are part of the design.</p>
          
